  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323410/extras/ed24d54b1e7e6590f45bea7f6fd5b615.avif?t=1684842883\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>Quest 4 Papa : Reloaded</strong> tells the story of Roach, a young girl who was bet as a child by his father, felling in the hands of The Scrappers, outcasts that dismount old droids for a living. Now, she’s all grow-up and looking to kick the ass of the one that dared to bet her, no matter who or what stands in her way.<br><br>Scrap and destroy tons of bots in a screw loose world and make your way to the slums of the city to reach your father and get sweet revenge!!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323410/extras/a40fc13b180859695c853dd6bb194d1f.avif?t=1684842883\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A world filled with sci-fi action:</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323410/extras/5971b65c2b8d58ff9ab392212707d3cd.poster.avif?t=1684842883\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323410/extras/5971b65c2b8d58ff9ab392212707d3cd.webm?t=1684842883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323410/extras/5971b65c2b8d58ff9ab392212707d3cd.mp4?t=1684842883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast-paced top down shooter gameplay:</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1323410/extras/244adb10e5bf06fc6fd877c375581968.poster.avif?t=1684842883\" width=600